Firayim Ministan Indiya zai halarci ginin haikalin a wurin da ake takaddama a kai
NEW DELHI (AP) - Firayim Ministan Indiya Narendra Modi zai halarci bikin kaddamar da wani gidan ibada na Hindu a wata mai zuwa a wani wurin da ake takaddama a arewacin Indiya inda masu tsatsauran ra&#39;ayin addinin Hindu suka rushe wani masallaci na karni na 16 a shekarar 1992, a cewar amintacciyar kungiyar. ginin Haikali.
An shirya bikin ne a ranar 5 ga watan Agusta, masu shirya kwanan wata sun ce yana da matukar amfani ga mabiya addinin Hindu amma kuma hakan ya cika shekara guda tun bayan da majalisar dokokin Indiya ta soke matakin cin gashin kanta na jiharta daya tilo da ke da rinjayen musulmi, wato Jammu da Kashmir.
Alamar ba zai yiwu a rasa ba ga duka magoya bayan Modi da masu adawa da Jam&#39;iyyar Bharatiya Janata ta Hindu mai kishin kasa, ko BJP, wanda littafinsa ya kwashe shekaru da yawa ya hada da alkawuran kwace ikon Kashmir da ke da alaka da gina haikali ga gunkin Hindu Ram inda masallacin zamanin Mughal ya ke. ya taba tsayawa, wani wuri a birnin Ayodhya na jihar Uttar Pradesh wanda masu ibada suka yi imani da zama wurin haifuwar Ram.
Saboda har yanzu coronavirus na ci gaba da yaduwa a duk fadin Indiya, wanda ya ba da rahoton bullar cutar ta uku mafi girma a duniya, za a watsa bikin kai tsaye ta gidan talabijin na kasar kuma adadin mahalarta da masu kallo za a iyakance, a cewar Vishwa Hindu Parishad, ko kungiyar Hindu ta Duniya. , wata kungiyar masu kishin addinin Hindu da ke kawance da BJP.
Haikalin zai kasance a matsayin &quot;cibiyar ci gaba mai dorewa kuma mara mutuwa ta daidaiton zamantakewa, haɗin kan ƙasa da haɗin kai da kuma farkar da tunanin Hindutva,&quot; ko kuma hanyar rayuwar Hindu, in ji mai magana da yawun kungiyar Vinod Bansal a cikin wata sanarwa ranar Asabar.
An dai warware takaddamar da aka kwashe tsawon karni ana yi kan wurin a bara bayan nasarar zaben da jam&#39;iyyar BJP ta samu.
A watan Nuwamba, Kotun Koli ta yanke hukuncin amincewa da amincewar haikalin, tana mai cewa za a ba da koke-koke na Musulmai kadada biyar a wani wuri na dabam.
Mabiya addinin Hindu masu tsaurin ra&#39;ayi sun dade suna jayayya cewa mahara musulmi Mughal sun gina wani masallaci a saman wani gidan ibada na tsohon birnin Ayodya.
Rikicin da ya barke a watan Disambar 1992 bayan rugujewar masallacin ya haifar da rikicin kabilanci inda aka kashe mutane kusan 2,000 galibinsu Musulmai.
