Sakatariyar Harkokin Cikin Gida Priti Patel ta bukaci bayani daga Twitter da Instagram kan tweets na Wiley &#39;abin kyama&#39;
Priti Patel ta bukaci bayani daga Twitter da Instagram na tsawon lokaci da aka dauka wajen cire wasu sakonnin &quot;abin kyama&quot; da Wiley ya yi.
A halin yanzu &#39;yan sanda suna gudanar da bincike kan jerin kalamai na nuna kyama da aka wallafa a shafukan sada zumunta na mawakin Grime.
Sakataren harkokin cikin gida ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter a ranar Lahadi cewa: &quot;Sabunta na nuna kyama daga Wiley abin kyama ne.&quot;
&quot;Bai kamata su ci gaba da zama a kan Twitter da Instagram na tsawon lokaci ba kuma na tambaye su cikakken bayani.&quot;
&quot;Kamfanonin kafofin watsa labarun dole ne su yi sauri da sauri don kawar da irin wannan mummunar ƙiyayya daga dandalin su.&quot;
An zargi Twitter da &quot;yin watsi da kyamar baki&quot; saboda har yanzu ana ganin sakonnin twitter na Wiley sa&#39;o&#39;i 12 da fara buga su.
Tuni dai aka cire wasu sakonnin twitter sannan kuma mai shekaru 41 da haifuwa ya haramtawa shafin na tsawon kwanaki bakwai.
A baya Twitter ya ce an kulle asusun Wiley na wani dan lokaci &quot;saboda karya manufofin mu na nuna kyama,&quot; yayin da Facebook ya ce &quot;babu wurin yin kalaman kiyayya a Instagram.&quot;
Rundunar &#39;yan sanda ta Biritaniya ta ce a ranar Asabar: &quot;The Met na daukar duk rahotannin nuna kyamar baki da muhimmanci. Ana tantance abubuwan da suka dace.&quot;
A halin yanzu, kamfanin sarrafa Wiley, A-List Management, &quot;yanke duk wata alaƙa&quot; tare da tauraro.
Tsohon manajan mai zanen, John Woolf, wanda Bayahude ne, ya rubuta a shafin Twitter cewa: &quot;Bayan tweets na kyamar Yahudawa a yau mu a @A_ListMGMT mun yanke duk wata alaka da shi. Babu wani wuri a cikin al&#39;umma don kyamar baki.&quot;
A baya dai ya ce bai goyi bayan ko amincewa da abin da Wiley ya wallafa ba amma zai yi magana da shi a asirce da kuma &quot;taimaka masa wajen ilmantar da shi.&quot;
Sai dai a wani faifan bidiyo a shafin Instagram, Wiley ya bayyana yana cewa shi ne ya yanke hulda da mahukuntan nasa.
Wasu &#39;yan majalisar sun soki Twitter saboda barin tweet din ya kasance a bayyane.
Dan majalisar jam&#39;iyyar Labour Jess Phillips ya fada a ranar Asabar:
&quot;Kawai an ga duk abubuwan Wiley. Me yasa @Twitter ya bar irin wannan kyama da ƙiyayya? Yana kaiwa duk wani haɗari mai haɗari, Yahudawa suna samun abubuwan da ba ku samu ba, suna da iko, suna tunanin mafi kyau ... Wannan abu ne mai hatsari, tabbas ya kamata ya sauko.&quot;
Wakilin dan majalisa Neil Coyle ya kara da cewa: &quot;Ayyukansa sun bayyana suna iya yin aiki da sauri fiye da @Twitter yana jaddada cewa doka (ciki har da Dokar Harms ta Yanar gizo) yakamata ta tabbatar da cewa ba a amfani da dandamalin kafofin watsa labarun don yada ƙiyayya.&quot;
John Mann, mashawarcin gwamnati mai zaman kansa kan kyamar baki, ya ce tweets &quot;sun nuna daidai dalilin da yasa doka ke buƙatar canza su don yin lissafi mai ma&#39;ana.&quot;
A halin da ake ciki kuma, Kamfen da Yahudanci ya bukaci ‘yan sanda da su binciki abubuwan da Wiley ke ciki tare da yin kira ga a rufe shafukansa na sada zumunta domin hana ci gaba da zubar dafin dafin yahudawa.
Wiley, wanda aka fi sani da Godfather na Grime kuma wanda ainihin sunansa Richard Cowie, ya sami MBE don sabis na kiɗa a cikin 2018.
&quot;Rashin kasawa&quot; na Amurka yana hana neman magungunan coronavirus
Yunkurin da duniya ke yi na samar da magunguna masu amfani da cutar ta Amurka na kawo cikas saboda masu bincike suna gwada magunguna ta hanyar &quot;ba da gangan ba,&quot; in ji masanin da ke jagorantar shirin na Burtaniya ya yi gargadin.
Shirin gwaji na farfadowa na Biritaniya, wanda ya hada da marasa lafiya 12,000 a asibitocin Burtaniya dari da dama, ya rigaya ya nuna wani sabon maganin da zai magance cutar sannan kuma ya bayyana wasu biyu - wadanda a baya ake tunanin za su iya ceton rai - a matsayin mara amfani.
Amma gazawar tsarin likitancin Amurka ya dace da wannan fitowar yana nufin cewa sauran jiyya masu ban sha&#39;awa waɗanda za a iya share su don amfani da yawa har yanzu ba a tantance su ba.
Musamman, plasma convalescent (plasma na jini wanda aka karɓa daga marasa lafiya na Covid-19 kuma yana ɗauke da ƙwayoyin rigakafi waɗanda zasu iya kare wasu daga cutar) har yanzu ana gwada su da kyau akan babban gwaji na bazuwar.
&quot;An riga an ba dubun dubatar mutane plasma convalescent plasma a Amurka amma ba a yi watsi da wadannan jiyya ba,&quot; in ji Farfesa Martin Landray, daya daga cikin wadanda suka kafa shirin farfadowa.
Landray, kwararre kan kafa manyan magunguna ya kara da cewa &quot;Suna ba wa daidaikun mutane plasma convalescent da fatan zai yi aiki. An ba da adadi mai yawa kuma har yanzu ba su da masaniya ko yana taimakawa ko cutarwa ko kuma ba shi da wani tasiri.&quot; gwaji.
Amurka ta kasa yin manyan gwaje-gwaje na bazuwar kuma hakan ya ƙare samar da miyagun ƙwayoyi.
Gwajin magunguna bazuwar sune ma&#39;aunin zinare don nuna magunguna masu amfani.
Suna cire son zuciya da ba su sani ba wanda zai iya rikitar da hukuncin likitocin.
Dubban mutane ne aka bai wa wani magani sannan kuma an baiwa dubban wasu magungunan placebo.
Babu wanda ya san wanda aka ba su.
Sa&#39;an nan kuma ana kwatanta sakamako kuma an bayyana tasirin maganin.
Ta wannan hanyar, farfadowa ya sami damar nuna cewa steroid dexamethasone ya rage mace-mace da kashi uku a cikin marasa lafiya na Covid-19 akan na&#39;urorin iska.
Har ila yau, ya nuna cewa maganin da ake yawan yaɗawa hydroxychloroquine - da kuma haɗin gwiwar magungunan lopinavir da ritonavir - ba su da wani tasiri wajen ceton rayukan marasa lafiya.
Mahimmanci waɗannan gwaje-gwajen suna buƙatar adadi mai yawa na marasa lafiya kuma babu asibiti ɗaya da ya isa irin wannan bincike.
Biritaniya tana da fa&#39;ida ɗaya ɗaya - cibiyar kula da Lafiya ta ƙasa.
Sabanin haka, sabis ɗin kiwon lafiyar Amurka ya rabu kuma nasarar da kawai ya samu wajen nuna yiwuwar magani shine yana nuna fa&#39;idar remdesivir mai tsadar gaske don saurin murmurewa na wasu marasa lafiya na Covid-19.
Landray ya kara da cewa &quot;Akwai kuri&#39;a da yawa na kananan gwaje-gwajen magunguna da suka hada da &#39;yan dozin ko &#39;yan majinyata da ke faruwa a Amurka amma babu wani abu,&quot; in ji Landray.
&quot;Suna kasa yin manyan gwaje-gwaje na bazuwar kuma hakan ya kawo karshen samar da magunguna marasa kyau. Yana sa aikin likitanci ya fi talauci kuma sakamakon marasa lafiya ya fi talauci.&quot;
Landray ya ce wannan gazawar ta kasance mai ban haushi musamman idan aka zo ga amfani da kwayar cutar plasma, wanda likitoci da yawa suka yi imanin na iya samun babbar rawar da za su taka wajen kula da masu fama da cutar ta Covid-19.
&quot;Idan ka dubi Amurka, an yi amfani da adadi mai yawa na wannan magani bisa ga son rai. Burtaniya ta yi fice fiye da ma&#39;auni idan aka kwatanta da abin da ke faruwa a can,&quot; in ji shi.
Farfesa Peter Horby, kwararre kan cututtuka masu yaduwa kuma wanda ya kafa shirin Farfadowa, ya ce: “An samu rahotannin majiyyata 20,000 da ke samun kwayar cutar plasma a cikin wata kungiya amma babu daya daga cikin wadanda suka kamu da cutar.
Idan da sun sanya waɗannan majinyata cikin gwaje-gwaje na bazuwar, da yanzu za mu sami cikakkiyar amsa game da tasirin plasma convalescent.&quot;
Horby ya kara da cewa farfadowar Burtaniya a yanzu ta kaddamar da gwajin bazuwar plasma na convalescent amma baya tsammanin sakamakon zai kasance a shirye har zuwa karshen wannan shekara.
