Pakistan na son Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta taka rawar da ta taka wajen warware matsalar Kashmir a karkashin kudurorinta ta hanyar kyale mutanen da ke zaune a yankin Himalayan su yanke shawarar ko suna son hadewa da Indiya, da Pakistan ko kuma sun fi son &#39;yancin kai.
